[I] KDE Frameworks addon for unit conversions

[T] KUnitConversion provides functions to convert values in different physical
[T] units. It supports converting different prefixes (e.g. kilo, mega, giga) as
[T] well as converting between different unit systems (e.g. liters, gallons).

[U] https://invent.kde.org/frameworks/kunitconversion

